Welcome to CoBrowse united.com!

During a phone conversation with an agent, we may be able to better assist you with CoBrowse, a customer support solution. CoBrowse will allow the agent to see what you see and answer your questions. They will only be able to see united.com - nothing else. Your personal information, such as credit card numbers and passwords, won't be visible to the agent. When you start a session with an agent, you agree to share your united.com browser window.
